Changed the Sync Devices From Network and Sync Network Data From Network jobs to require both hostname and serial to match an existing Nautobot Device by default; devices with a drifted serial are now skipped with a warning rather than having their serial silently rewritten. The new `Update Devices With Changed Serial` toggle (default OFF) restores hostname-only matching within the job's filter scope, required for Virtual Chassis where the chassis-level serial changes when the stack master role moves between members.
